OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FA man has been jailed after breaching
OL,8,Fhis Criminal Behaviour Order in front
OL,9,Fof a plain-clothed police officer.
OL,11,FRobert Mallaburn, aged 45, was banned
OL,12,Fin 2021 from begging for money
OL,13,Fanywhere and Ashfield, after
OL,14,Frepeatedly harassing shoppers and
OL,15,Fretail staff.
OL,17,FMallaburn, who is also prohibited from
OL,18,Fusing aggressive, abusive or
OL,19,Fthreatening words or behaviour, was
OL,20,Fseen asking people for money in on
OL,21,FSaturday 18 May.
