OL,7,FHe then asked the officer directly for
OL,8,Fmoney and was arrested a short time
OL,9,Flater.
OL,11,FMallaburn, of Lansbury Road,
OL,12,FEdwinstowe, was charged with three
OL,13,Fcounts of breaching a Criminal
OL,14,FBehaviour Order.
OL,16,FThe other counts relate to incidents
OL,17,Fof begging outside Sainsbury's, in
OL,18,FMansfield Road, on 13 and 15 May.
