OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FAppearing at Nottingham Magistrates'
OL,8,FCourt on Monday, 20 May, he pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to the charges and was jailed
OL,10,Ffor a total of 16 weeks.
OL,12,FSergeant Alice Bartle, of
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "This is
OL,14,Fthe second time Malliburn has breached
OL,15,Fthis order and it is of little
OL,16,Fsurprise that he's been jailed as a
OL,17,Fresult.
