OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,F"Criminal Behaviour Orders of this
OL,8,Fnature are not granted lightly by the
OL,9,Fcourts, who take an extremely negative
OL,10,Fview of anyone who breaches them.
OL,12,F"Aggressive and nuisance begging is a
OL,13,Fblight on our public spaces and is not
OL,14,Fsomething that we will overlook.
OL,16,F"Where possible we will direct people
OL,17,Fto any help and support they need, but
OL,18,Fultimately we will take decisive
OL,19,Faction when all other options have
OL,20,Fbeen exhausted.
